name: Genealogy of Hesperides Nymphs
description:
THE HESPERIDES were the goddess-nymphs of the evening and the golden light of sunsets. The Hesperides were entrusted with the care of wild animals and the tree of the golden apples. The seven nymphs and their glowing, golden apples were regarded as the source of the golden light of sunset

Style: fantasy , fairy tale
Genre: mixed media art
Media: watercolor
Size: 3500 x 2625 px
